text: Irina Demick (16 October 1936 – 8 October 2004), sometimes credited as Irina Demich, was a French actress. She was known for her roles in OSS se déchaîne (1963), The Visit (1964), Un monsieur de compagnie (1964) and Up from the Beach (1965). ==Other websites== * Category:1936 births Category:2004 deaths Category:French movie actors Category:French television actors Category:French stage actors
